        <text>
            <body> <p>Ego <persName key="d1e13694" xml:id="d1e137721">Bernardus, dictus abbas
                                <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e137723">Fonten(etensis)</orgName>
                        </persName>, per hujus <sic corresp="#A1">cyrophi</sic> scriptum notum facio
                            <lb n="2"/> universis quod domina <persName key="d1e13700" xml:id="d1e137731">Aalaiz de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324373" xml:id="d1e137733">Asneriis</placeName>
                        </persName>, laudante <persName key="d1e13706" xml:id="d1e137736">Margarita</persName> filia sua, dedit in perpetu<lb n="3" break="no"/>am elemosinam ecclesie nostre de <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e137742">Fonten(eto)</orgName> pro salute anime sue quartam
                        partem decime bla<lb n="4" break="no"/>di apud <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324350" xml:id="d1e137747">Raverias</placeName>, quam de
                        proprio alodio suo ibi possidebat, et de hoc adversus omnes homines <lb n="5"/> nobis garantiam portabit. Nos vero intuitu caritatis et pacis
                        dabimus ei annuatim ad <lb n="6"/> festum Sancti Remigii quamdiu vixerit et
                        ubicumque fuerit .L. solidos illius monete que cursalis <lb n="7"/> erit in
                        terra ducis. Insuper fecimus eam participem omnium beneficiorum que fient in
                            do<lb n="8" break="no"/>mo nostra et plenarium servicium ei in obitu suo
                        sicut uni monachorum nostrorum persolvemus. <lb n="9"/> Hujus rei testes
                        sunt <persName key="d1e13712" xml:id="d1e137761">Humbertus
                            grangiarius</persName>, <persName key="d1e13718" xml:id="d1e137764">Hugo
                            cellerarius</persName>, <persName key="d1e13724" xml:id="d1e137767">Adam</persName> monachi nostri, <persName key="d1e13731" xml:id="d1e137771">Leo<lb n="10" break="no"/>nardus presbiter de
                                <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324475" xml:id="d1e137775">Marmania</placeName>
                        </persName>, <persName key="d1e13737" xml:id="d1e137778">Girardus de
                                <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324373" xml:id="d1e137780">Asneriis</placeName>
                        </persName>, maritus prefate <persName key="d1e13743" xml:id="d1e137783">Margarite</persName>, <persName key="d1e13749" xml:id="d1e137786">Teobaudus <lb n="11"/> prepositus de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324487" xml:id="d1e137790">Monte Barro</placeName>
                        </persName>. Ad cujus rei memoriam sigillum meum cyrographo presenti appo<lb n="12" break="no"/>sui.</p>
                
            </body>
